    <text>
        <body>
        	<div1 type="letter">
        		<pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0083"/>
        		<head>Jim to Mlle. Marcelle Guerin <date value="1915-06-12">Jun12’15</date></head>
        		
        		<opener>
            <dateline><date value="1915-06-12">Jun12’15</date></dateline>
        		</opener>
        		
            <p>
            Barnum &amp; Bailey’s big four
            ring tent show has anchored
            someplace near <unclear>Goul [sp?]</unclear>.  About
            thirty kilometers from the
            front.  Our Chief went over
            to see them yesterday.
            There are no patients in it
            yet.  Its sweltering in
            the day and chilly at night.
            The crowd is disgusted
            and the leaders do not
            pull together.  The flags,
            however, are flying
            merrily and the sight
            must please the small
                        
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0084a" n="[p.2]"/>
            
            boys.  “All kinds candy,
            peanuts, and popcorn!”
            That’s a fool crowd
            down in the hospital.
            Wouldn’t you know
            the Mc Adoo kid would
            quit.  Just like her
            type.  Wants to play
            nurse because she
            thinks its smart.
            </p><p>
            Paul is back 
            in Paris now.  Kiffin
            is doing very well
            
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0084b"/>
            
            and may be moved to 
            the city.  Had an interesting
            morning walk in the
            bois near here before 
            breakfast.  The other 
            noises seem queer when
            one hears birds chirping.
            </p><p>
            //Bis B’d Debssert seems
            to be a great friend
            of mine.  Hear [sic] quite often.
            </p>
        		
        		<closer>
            <salute>Pretty quiet around
            here now.</salute>
            
            <signed>Jim</signed>
        		</closer>
        		
            <!-- [This letter and envelope are all of a piece. It is addressed to: Mlle. Marcelle Guerin, Salle 69, Ambulance Americaine, Neuilly-ssur-Seine.] -->
            
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0086"/>
            
            </div1>
        </body>
